{"tid":985830,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"安達臣道7私樓用地改建公營屋","createTime":"2019-01-18T03:01:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T11:19:28.000Z","uid":56881,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"df59b0c8e4116941bf9ac2e21f65e381c7fff4a5","tid":985830,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T03:01:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/EgrYvnazs2K5kHu3e1RfGg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/thesun.hk.com/3b245c6cdc45be864c4e3481f9ce2151\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FEgrYvnazs2K5kHu3e1RfGg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fthesun.hk.com%2F3b245c6cdc45be864c4e3481f9ce2151&h=3c234f85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因應公營房屋需求殷切，政府先後將七幅位於安達臣道石礦場的私樓用地撥作公營房屋用途，預計於二○二四至二六年陸續落成，房屋署代表昨於西貢區議會交代詳情時透露，七幅土地將全部撥作興建資助出售房屋，但會保留調撥作出租公屋的彈性。多名區議員則擔心區內人口大增，交通會進一步逼爆，違泊等問題有機會惡化，促請當局做好配套，「只係為起樓而起樓，將會係悲劇！」<br />\n<br />\n安達臣道石礦場將有七幅私營土地轉作公營房屋用途，房屋協會及房委會分別佔三幅及四幅，合共提供六千七百個單位，容納一萬九千人居住。<br />\n<br />\n房署：或會改為出租公屋<br />\n<br />\n房署高級建築師孫惠民在會上指，安達臣石礦場的公私營房屋比例為九比一，現計劃將該七幅地全部撥作資助出售房屋，因為附近已有不少出租公屋，但日後需求若果有改變，亦不排除可轉出租公屋。<br />\n<br />\n多名區議員擔心大量單位入伙後交通嚴重擠塞。區議員李家良指將軍澳發展後的車位已非常不足，預計安達臣石礦場新發展的七幅土地同樣面對該問題，雖然有關新發展區設有綠化區及人工湖，但交通不便，擔心會淪為「私人後花園」，即使附近的居民亦難以享用。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%AE%89%E9%81%94%E8%87%A3%E9%81%937%E7%A7%81%E6%A8%93%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E6%94%B9%E5%BB%BA%E5%85%AC%E7%87%9F%E5%B1%8B-214500379.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25AE%2589%25E9%2581%2594%25E8%2587%25A3%25E9%2581%25937%25E7%25A7%2581%25E6%25A8%2593%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%259C%25B0%25E6%2594%25B9%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%2585%25AC%25E7%2587%259F%25E5%25B1%258B-214500379.html&d=fU3nvaAexaWFGJTF6lGlK9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=4148096d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%AE%89%E9%81%94%E8%87%A3%E9%81%937%E7%A7%81%E6%A8%93%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%B0%E6%94%B9%E5%BB%BA%E5%85%AC%E7%87%9F%E5%B1%8B-214500379.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db9461de04ab87c27468508cb31dd9d325988189","tid":985830,"uid":77569,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T03:07:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fa50e54ccb2f56d394236e12d78aef1709e3c47d","tid":985830,"uid":52003,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T03:08:32.000Z","msg":"正常有工返邊可能申請到公屋?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16bb1c323b36b9de4be4fc5262b6bc8a7e35d5f2","tid":985830,"uid":33868,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T03:09:35.000Z","msg":"究竟安達臣會有幾多人住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成個蝗蟲區咁，個面積大過成個觀塘市中心"},{"pid":"206e304d566aa3753bb5898aa77862aa5ebcd494","tid":985830,"uid":57549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16bb1c323b36b9de4be4fc5262b6bc8a7e35d5f2","tid":985830,"uid":33868,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T03:09:35.000Z","msg":"究竟安達臣會有幾多人住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成個蝗蟲區咁，個面積大過成個觀塘市中心"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T03:10:39.000Z","msg":"第二個水泉澳"},{"pid":"795a020461d510d8d6bb28e4ccc563e357ca5c37","tid":985830,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"206e304d566aa3753bb5898aa77862aa5ebcd494","tid":985830,"uid":57549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16bb1c323b36b9de4be4fc5262b6bc8a7e35d5f2","tid":985830,"uid":33868,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T03:09:35.000Z","msg":"究竟安達臣會有幾多人住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成個蝗蟲區咁，個面積大過成個觀塘市中心"},